name: digital familiar
description: sigil ten. traditionally, familiars are known as supernatural entities that assist cunning folk in their practice of magic. they can manifest in numerous forms, usually as an animal, other times as a human or humanoid figure. in modern technomancy, familiars are our digital avatars, or whatever form we choose to represent ourselves online. what do you think your familiar gets up to once you log off? collect to attract loyalty. inscribed by tenorless circa 2019 // genesis collection
